TableDefinition.DatabaseQuery: SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY dbo.GetFullFilePath(%NTFS2db_col_id%,f.ID)) as 'id', dbo.GetFullFilePath(%NTFS2db_col_id%,f.ID) as 'NTFS-object', a_owner.Name as 'Owner', t_owner.Text as 'Owner-type', a_ace.Name as 'Permission', t_ace.Text as 'Permission-type', ISNULL(ace_m_v.Text, 'Special') as 'Mask' FROM GetFilesByCollID(%NTFS2db_col_id%) f INNER JOIN SecurityDescriptors sd ON f.SdID = sd.ID INNER JOIN Sids s_owner ON s_owner.ID = sd.OwnerSidID LEFT JOIN GetAccountsByCollID(%NTFS2db_col_id%) a_owner ON a_owner.SidID = s_owner.ID LEFT JOIN AccountTypes t_owner ON t_owner.Type = a_owner.Type LEFT JOIN Acls acl ON acl.ID = sd.DaclID LEFT JOIN AclsVsAces a_a ON a_a.AclID = acl.ID LEFT JOIN Aces ace ON ace.ID = a_a.AceID LEFT JOIN Sids s_ace ON s_ace.ID = ace.SidID LEFT JOIN AceMaskValues ace_m_v ON ace_m_v.Value = ace.Mask LEFT JOIN GetAccountsByCollID(%NTFS2db_col_id%) a_ace ON a_ace.SidID = s_ace.ID LEFT JOIN AccountTypes t_ace ON t_ace.Type = a_ace.Type WHERE NOT ((t_owner.Text = 'WellKnown' OR a_owner.Name = 'Administrators' OR a_owner.Name = 'Administrator' OR a_owner.Name = 'Domain Admins') AND (t_ace.Text = 'WellKnown' OR a_ace.Name = 'Administrators' OR a_ace.Name = 'Administrator' OR a_ace.Name = 'Domain Admins')) AND NOT ace.Flags & 16 = 16 ORDER BY f.Name
